.TH degrees "1" "February 2019" "SMI Toolset 0.100.0" "SMI Math Command"
.SH NAME
degrees \- Convert radians to degrees
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B degrees
.I RADIANS
.SH DESCRIPTION
.PP
.B degrees
